Job Description 
Mobile App Test engineer

Job Requirements 
-	About 1-3 years App testing experience
-	Familiar with OS of IOS/Android 
-	Has capability to handle App testing project independently
-	Be good at least MySQL
-	Be Familiar with API Testing
-	Be Familiar tools of sniffer packet, eg.  Flidder	
-	Has capability to implement project in high pressure

Keywords in the resume
Automation testing, performance testing
